  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tLast week, we&rsquo;ve reviewed some familiar products which are gradually fading away from our life, such as Kodak film, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/feature phones\" target=\"_blank\">feature phones</a>, man-powered bike and radio. Someone said that this is a normal <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/phase-out\" target=\"_blank\">phase-out</a> process for these products because the creative and human beings are <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/relentlessly\" target=\"_blank\">relentlessly</a> inventing more fashionable gadgets to replace outdated ones.</p>\n<p>\n\tHowever, when you carefully read our life, you may notice that some <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/vintage\" target=\"_blank\">vintage</a> things stubbornly survive and resist the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/erosion\" target=\"_blank\">erosion</a> of those <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/glittering\" target=\"_blank\">glittering</a> advanced technology. There are irreplaceable <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/carrier\" target=\"_blank\">carrier</a> of our time, our emotion and our idea &ndash; <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/analog\" target=\"_blank\">analog</a>&nbsp;clock, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/vinyl\" target=\"_blank\">vinyl</a>&nbsp;recordand pen respectively.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t- Why these three things are still here without discarded by us?</p>\n<p>\n\t- Are there other things bravely resist the attack of the advanced technologies?</p>\n<p>\n\t- DIY topic about irreplaceable things.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe vinyl record has a longer history than my life. When I was a child, I was told the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/cassette\" target=\"_blank\">cassette</a> will replace the vinyl record. But it didn&rsquo;t. Later, when I was teenager, I thought the hand-set CD player would sweep both vinyl record and cassette into the dustbin. Surprisingly, it didn&rsquo;t too. Lastly, when I was in college, it seems that mp3 player would like to eat them all together. Unfortunately, like its <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/predecessor\" target=\"_blank\">predecessor</a>, mp3 player haven&rsquo;t fulfilled his mission too.<br />\n\tIn the digital age, the vinyl record has seen a revival with music hardcore fans who collect or buy vinyl for the coolness factor, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/nostalgia\" target=\"_blank\">nostalgia</a> or just because I love it blindly. To me, the chief strength of vinyl is the flip side of its chief weakness - you can not take it away. Every other music format can be listened portably, but vinyl record can&rsquo;t. Similarly, there are always some immovable memories in our heart. They&rsquo;re just laid at there silently, untouchably but unforgettably. Sometimes, when we are fatigued about the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/hustle\" target=\"_blank\">hustle</a> and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bustle\" target=\"_blank\">bustle</a> society, listen to the vinyl record in a fixed place could make you peaceful.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/846775/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p570318/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p570318\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p567374/\">当天才遇上天才：卷福和谢耳朵的10个共同点</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p568801/\">美国淡定哥爆红网络：坠机落海后不忘自拍</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p562036/\">拒绝穷忙：每天上班做这10件事就够了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p562541/\">海外视角：大学假期里该做的几件事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p568707/\">世界最烂蜡像馆走红 没一个和真人像</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p570151/\">点赞需谨慎：美国男子因点\"赞\"被捕</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p566963/\">享受周末时光：成功人士是如何过周末的</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p570127/\">网友热议奥斯卡提名：进击吧莱昂纳多！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p568366/\">有爱组图：萌娃与萌宠的欢乐时光</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 